    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your<strong> sirloin steak[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper, then drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> on both sides</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1621.-step-5-x200.jpg",
