          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1621.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the steaks are resting, chop your <strong>baby plum tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> in a large bowl</p><p>Once ready to serve, add your <strong>salad</strong> and the<strong> halved tomatoes</strong> to the bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
