            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once rested, slice the <strong>steak[s] </strong>on a clean board</p><p>Serve the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>steak</strong> with the <strong>sweet potato wedges</strong> and<strong> tomato salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>chimichurri</strong> all over the steak</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
